      "description": "Calling all DIY enthusiasts and project lovers! This car is ready for a total transformation and offers a fantastic starting point for someone looking to roll up their sleeves. It\u2019s currently in poor condition and will need significant mechanical work and some serious TLC to get back into shape, but it\u2019s a wonderful opportunity to build something great from the ground up!",
