    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive care: a garage-kept, single-owner masterpiece in showroom condition. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish protected by a professional ceramic coating, showing absolutely no swirl marks, rock chips, or door dings. Inside, the cabin remains in a time-capsule state; the premium leather upholstery is supple and free of any wear or creasing, and the original factory scent persists. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the climate control, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, this vehicle is beyond reproach, boasting a meticulous full-service history performed exclusively at the authorized dealership. It rides on pristine original alloy wheels wrapped in brand-new performance tires. With remarkably low mileage and a clean title in hand, this is the perfect opportunity for a discerning buyer seeking a vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it left the showroom floor. No accidents, no pets, and no compromises.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
